-- Canadian Dollar Weakens After Poloz Named Central-Bank Chief
-- B y   G r e g   S t o r e y
-- 2013-05-02T20:23:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-02/canadian-dollar-weakens-after-poloz-named-central-bank-chief.html
Canada’s dollar weakened after Stephen
Poloz, the head of the nation’s export-financing agency, was
named to lead the Bank of Canada, succeeding  Mark Carney , who
will take over at the Bank of England.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
